name: Roy Tang
text: Thanks for the info MarisBarney Garcia! In the interest of fairness, I'll edit this info into the post above. This is just the feedback I was hoping for; I'll trust your word on this 😃. I already found a video of the speech this morning, but seeing as how they're all one hour long, tinatamad pa ako panoorin. (I have trouble paying attention to his ramblings for an extended period 😛)
